Cook pasta as directed on package, omitting salt and adding peas to the water for the last 2 min. Meanwhile, heat oil in large nonstick skillet on medium-high heat. Add asparagus, peppers and garlic; cook and stir 3 to 4 min. or until vegetables are crisp-tender. Add Cooking Creme; cook and stir 2 to 3 min. or until heated through. Drain pasta mixture, reserving 1/3 cup cooking water. Gradually add reserved water to sauce mixture until desired consistency is reached. Add pasta; mix lightly. Serve immediately.